snippet.title: Instinction - Announcement Trailer "The Anticipation" - Future Games Show E3 2021
snippet.description:
Instinction by Hashbane is a narratively driven action-adventure game. In this World Premiere trailer you can get a first look at the terrifyingly immersive combat and exploration in multiple awe-inspiring locations​.
Instinction will have an initial release on PC and subsequent releases on PS4+5 and Xbox Series X+S. Google Stadia and Nintendo Switch versions are also being considered.
